() Tj T*
(Finding #1: [High] Lower bound time manipulation risk in options.spend) Tj T*
(  Detector: missing-validity-range) Tj T*
(  Module: options) Tj T*
(  Location: validators/options.ak:696) Tj T*
(Description: Handler uses get_lower_bound for time-sensitive logic with field\(s\)) Tj T*
(    [deadline] but never checks the upper bound. An attacker can set the lower bound) Tj T*
(    arbitrarily far in the past, manipulating time-based calculations \(interest accrual,) Tj T*
(    fee computation, deadline checks\).) Tj T*
(Recommendation: Use get_upper_bound instead of get_lower_bound for time-sensitive) Tj T*
(    calculations. The upper bound cannot be set arbitrarily into the past.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Finding #2: [High] Unsafe match\(..., >=\) value comparison in options.spend) Tj T*
(  Detector: unsafe-match-comparison) Tj T*
(  Module: options) Tj T*
(  Location: validators/options.ak:696) Tj T*
(Description: Handler options.spend uses `match` for Value comparison. The `>=` operator) Tj T*
(    only verifies Lovelace sufficiency and may miss native token imbalances, allowing) Tj T*
(    over-lending or protocol insolvency.) Tj T*
(Recommendation: Replace `match\(..., >=\)` with explicit per-asset quantity checks. Use) Tj T*
(    `value.without_lovelace` for exact token matching or check individual asset quantities) Tj T*
(    directly.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Finding #3: [High] Unsafe match\(..., >=\) value comparison in options.mint) Tj T*
(  Detector: unsafe-match-comparison) Tj T*
(  Module: options) Tj T*
(  Location: validators/options.ak:760) Tj T*
